                        register the items you would reuse. Visit our "Registering Items" section below to kickstart the recycling adventure!
                    </p>
                    <a href="CreateItem" class="btn btn-primary">Registering Items</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card text-center">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Take items Home Made Easy</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        You found something amazing? lovely Take it home! this is made easy by our "Take Home" Section Just input the item ID and click take home!.
